TITLE: Initializing Formbricks Widget in JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet demonstrates how to import the Formbricks library and initialize the widget in your main component. It includes a check for the window object to ensure it's running in a browser environment. The setup method requires an environment ID and app URL.
SOURCE: https://github.com/formbricks/formbricks/blob/main/packages/js-core/README.md#2025-04-11_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
