TITLE: Configuring Traefik HTTP to HTTPS Redirection
DESCRIPTION: YAML configuration for Traefik that sets up HTTP to HTTPS redirection and defines secure entry points. This ensures all traffic is encrypted with SSL.
SOURCE: https://github.com/formbricks/formbricks/blob/main/docs/self-hosting/configuration/custom-ssl.mdx#2025-04-11_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: yaml
CODE:
```
entryPoints:
  web:
    address: ":80"
    http:
      redirections:
        entryPoint:
          to: websecure
          scheme: https
          permanent: true
  websecure:
    address: ":443"

providers:
  docker:
    watch: true
    exposedByDefault: false
  file:
    directory: /etc/traefik/dynamic
```

